name: Mythology GEMINI Zodiac
description:
Castor & Pollux are twin brothers.
Has the same mother, namely Leda.
But dad is different.
These twins grew up handsome.
Having adventurous nature & close relationship.
Castor died in a battle.
Pollux is in great desperation and asks his father Zeus to revoke his immortality.
But Zeus chose to make Castor immortal as well.
